title: The Vegan Runners Cafe - Food Bike
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Western, Fast food, Bakery, Take-out only
description: Bicycle vendor selling vegan burgers in Udon Thani's Nong Prajak park, here since March 2016 The buns are baked with a mixture of whole wheat and bread flour. Patties are from a company which specializes in vegan mockmeat. Egg-less mayonaise is used. After closing hours you could join running in the park but contact in advance.
